This paper belongs to the field of Natural Language Processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on Automatic Text Summarization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the algorithm involves ranking sentences based on their relevance to the document topic and vocabulary, which suggests that it may also fall under the sub-categories of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE).
